      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think it is not super obvious that we pin the step base on the step name only (there may be many ways to implement the pinning: step name or (builder/step name) or (build-step name). So I think we want to make it clear in the tooltip that it will also apply to a step with the same name in different builder).\n\nIs there a specific reason you want to apply the settings to a global step name, rather than only to the step of the current builder?",
